original_title: Persona Super Live P-Sound Street 2019 〜Q番シアターへようこそ〜
overview: Welcome to the PERSONA SUPER LIVE P-SOUND STREET 2019 -Q Theater” was held at Ryogoku Kokugikan for two days on April 24 (Wednesday) and 25 (Thursday), 2019. “PERSONA SUPER LIVE P-SOUND STREET 2019 - Welcome to the Qth Theater” was held at the Yokohama Arena in 2017 at the “PERSONA SUPER LIVE P-SOUND BOMB! It was a long-awaited large-scale live for the first time in about two years.
title: Persona Super Live P-Sound Street 2019 - Welcome To Q Theater
